{"tid":753196,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人為甚麼愛旅遊？","createTime":"2018-07-23T11:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T12:48:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b4284cf3ab9d72549d9c5271c079a4e4a50ac9cf","tid":753196,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:50:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180723/20457141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F20457141&d=aYSZWfyDJHTTrJhvohPP0AtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=24c2ab3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F20457141&h=ce253f80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180723/20457141</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人為甚麼愛旅遊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180723/large/e88aa10a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180723%2Flarge%2Fe88aa10a.jpg&h=9e619e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《飲食男女》圖片<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一份調查報告指出香港人有多麼熱愛旅遊，接受調查的4372人中，只有10%的人不會每年都外出旅行，其他人，每年旅行次數由1次至5次不等，更有11%的人多過5次。平均每年外遊2次的人佔了多數，達28%；每年外遊3次的人，也有17%之多。<br />\n<br />\n廉航的興起，為港人外遊創造了條件。但是，即使沒有廉航，相信香港人還是喜歡旅遊，一有假期，必定想離開香港。調查報告如果問港人，「你究竟是喜歡外遊，還是渴望離開香港？」答案一定相當有趣。<br />\n<br />\n有讀者一針見血地指出，「當買樓、移民無望，每天出街會見到一街不想見到的人，打開電視會看到不想看到的新聞，旅行，是香港人逃避可悲現實的唯一缺口，是人生中一點點小確幸。」很悲哀，但是很真實。也有移民外國的讀者留言說，在香港的時候，他一有假期就想離開香港，無論去甚麼國家都好，總之一定要外出「唞氣」，但是移居北美洲後，他開始享受居家生活，一有假期，就在家中放鬆地休息。<br />\n<br />\n香港人平時壓力巨大，放假若仍然留在香港，一家數口擠在三數百呎空間，只會令人窒息。外出則無論大街、商場、山野、海灘&hellip;&hellip;一律人頭湧湧。在香港，根本沒有辦法身心放鬆。<br />\n<br />\n有一個周五，朋友放工後直接去機場坐夜機飛東京，她說周末要「放鬆一下」，我問她兩天時間飛來飛去豈不是更累，她說不，「只要一離開香港，我就身心都舒服了。」  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=aYSZWfyDJHTTrJhvohPP0AtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=b5461f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n心理測試 (楊靜)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n所望於劉霞者 (古德明)"},{"pid":"054ce85bd2b79568de20f68de28cc4a6a84c5404","tid":753196,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"宜家去日本周街都要對住班不死鳥香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee9d6b7122ea6ce7924520c14c79d5f441e7a80","tid":753196,"uid":31355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"054ce85bd2b79568de20f68de28cc4a6a84c5404","tid":753196,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"宜家去日本周街都要對住班不死鳥香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8423bb8e124cf7b9b09fbf455c0ce8b395c0808","tid":753196,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ee9d6b7122ea6ce7924520c14c79d5f441e7a80","tid":753196,"uid":31355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"054ce85bd2b79568de20f68de28cc4a6a84c5404","tid":753196,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"宜家去日本周街都要對住班不死鳥香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T12:32:22.000Z","msg":"doughnut<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937315c1909dded20e461d88a5ebc9462d568fca","tid":753196,"uid":12449,"like":4,"